WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 28=

01:43.990 --> 01:46.340
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

01:46.340 --> 01:47.180
Simu,

01:47.470 --> 01:49.140
if you had exposed it later,

01:49.470 --> 01:50.550
I would have believed

01:50.550 --> 01:51.390
it was my own story.

01:51.830 --> 01:52.990
I haven't seen you for days.

01:52.990 --> 01:53.830
I just wanted to see

01:53.830 --> 01:55.420
how you would surprise me.

01:57.860 --> 01:58.780
What makes you

01:59.030 --> 02:00.060
collect stories here?

02:00.910 --> 02:02.750
I've always been fond
of listening to stories.

02:03.420 --> 02:04.300
Didn't you know?

02:06.940 --> 02:09.020
There are plenty of stories in the Void.

02:09.460 --> 02:10.790
Why do you waste time and energy

02:10.790 --> 02:12.350
listening to the mortals' trivialities?

02:13.070 --> 02:15.140
Those are even stories of resentment.

02:15.790 --> 02:17.180
I love those stories

02:17.740 --> 02:18.830
that are vivid

02:19.300 --> 02:20.740
with a life of their own.

02:24.990 --> 02:25.900
Simu, you...

02:27.390 --> 02:28.550
You want to be human?

02:34.900 --> 02:36.510
Do you want me to be that?

02:44.550 --> 02:45.860
There's too much work in the Void.

02:46.140 --> 02:47.550
Why did you suddenly come to see me?

02:51.390 --> 02:52.230
Three layers

02:52.900 --> 02:54.020
of unknown zones popped up

02:54.020 --> 02:54.900
in the Void Valley.

02:55.110 --> 02:56.950
I accidentally broke
the outermost layer.

02:58.300 --> 03:00.140
So I came here to confirm

03:00.700 --> 03:02.550
whether you trapped Bai Sanxing

03:03.390 --> 03:04.270
in the Valley.

03:06.140 --> 03:07.180
In that case,

03:07.740 --> 03:08.860
I need to work with Jiang Ai

03:09.510 --> 03:11.020
to repair the outermost layer.

03:12.420 --> 03:14.550
We must never let him get away again.

03:18.110 --> 03:19.180
He isn't in there.

03:21.460 --> 03:22.300
That's where I keep

03:22.300 --> 03:23.900
the belongings of the former sovereign

03:24.620 --> 03:25.790
just in memory of him.

03:26.950 --> 03:28.390
If you want to get in there,

03:29.110 --> 03:30.460
I'll let you in.

03:32.180 --> 03:34.270
So it's for the memory
of you and your father.

03:34.790 --> 03:35.700
Sorry for the offense.

03:36.110 --> 03:36.950
It doesn't matter.

03:37.950 --> 03:38.830
I put you in charge

03:38.840 --> 03:40.020
of all the affairs.

03:40.550 --> 03:41.990
It's good to be cautious.

03:42.350 --> 03:43.300
My Lady,

03:43.900 --> 03:45.390
Young Master Xu deeply admires you.

03:45.700 --> 03:46.620
He's here to see you.

03:47.140 --> 03:47.980
Miss He,

03:48.350 --> 03:49.190
sorry to bother you.

03:51.580 --> 03:52.620
She is

03:53.620 --> 03:55.860
all mine tonight.

04:01.460 --> 04:02.300
Don't mess around.

04:02.300 --> 04:03.180
Your father will know.

04:03.180 --> 04:04.020
You stay out of this.

04:11.180 --> 04:12.020
Where's she?

04:28.060 --> 04:28.940
Is she still here?

04:37.500 --> 04:38.710
She doesn't want to see you.

04:41.380 --> 04:42.470
Does she not want to see me?

04:43.940 --> 04:45.500
Or do you not dare to let her see me?

04:48.990 --> 04:50.230
You're a general,

04:50.820 --> 04:52.620
but you act like a lovelorn husband.

04:53.060 --> 04:54.300
How funny.

04:55.940 --> 04:56.940
Try something else.

04:57.740 --> 04:58.860
Provocation won't work on me.

04:59.790 --> 05:00.630
Or...

05:02.740 --> 05:03.860
We can make a bet.

05:04.910 --> 05:06.110
Haven't you wanted me dead?

05:07.150 --> 05:08.060
Then let's fight.

05:09.260 --> 05:10.100
If I win,

05:10.500 --> 05:11.550
you tell me where she is.

05:12.380 --> 05:13.220
If I lose,

05:13.820 --> 05:14.820
you'll be satisfied.

05:20.860 --> 05:21.790
You're not worthy.

05:23.380 --> 05:24.220
You don't dare?

05:26.470 --> 05:27.910
You have a death wish.

05:29.300 --> 05:30.740
Without spirit power,

05:31.420 --> 05:32.590
you may not be a match for me.

05:37.820 --> 05:39.150
Then I'll give you what you want.

05:59.300 --> 06:00.140
Oh, I forgot.

06:01.500 --> 06:02.380
You can't feel pain.

06:24.790 --> 06:25.860
You saw the 22 graves,

06:25.860 --> 06:26.790
didn't you?

06:27.300 --> 06:29.180
Are you so eager to be the 23rd?

06:29.710 --> 06:31.420
Maybe there will be a 24th

06:31.420 --> 06:32.300
and a 25th.

06:33.380 --> 06:35.110
No one can truly have her.

06:35.940 --> 06:36.910
Now, she could be

06:36.910 --> 06:37.910
sitting in some corner,

06:38.380 --> 06:40.380
mocking your foolish infatuation!

06:40.910 --> 06:41.990
You've been crazy about her

06:41.990 --> 06:42.860
for over 300 years.

06:43.590 --> 06:44.710
So what have you really got?

06:57.710 --> 06:58.550
Young Master Xu?

06:58.740 --> 07:00.110
- Yeah.
- Don't just stand there.

07:00.110 --> 07:00.950
Get him up!

07:11.150 --> 07:12.350
Is that all you've got?

07:16.030 --> 07:17.030
She wouldn't care

07:17.670 --> 07:18.910
whether you live or die.

07:27.350 --> 07:28.300
Like I said,

07:29.470 --> 07:30.350
you aren't worthy.

07:58.670 --> 07:59.510
My bet paid off.

08:33.380 --> 08:34.620
You keep seeking pleasure.

08:35.660 --> 08:36.620
You're an official.

08:37.860 --> 08:39.740
But you fought for a top beauty!

08:40.620 --> 08:41.470
Who in this city

08:42.260 --> 08:43.140
doesn't know

08:43.380 --> 08:44.620
you have feelings for Miss Wang?

08:45.310 --> 08:47.470
Will Duke Pei just let you

08:47.470 --> 08:48.500
marry her?

08:48.950 --> 08:49.790
And Fang Xianye!

08:50.660 --> 08:52.230
He fights you on everything!

08:52.740 --> 08:54.380
And you ruined your own reputation!

08:54.950 --> 08:55.790
You've disgraced

08:56.350 --> 08:57.660
our whole family!

09:03.740 --> 09:04.580
From this day on,

09:05.740 --> 09:07.070
behave yourself and prepare

09:07.500 --> 09:08.340
for the wedding.

09:09.140 --> 09:09.980
I'll handle

09:10.900 --> 09:11.860
all the other things!

09:30.860 --> 09:32.620
I requested His Majesty to approve

09:32.620 --> 09:34.500
your marriage to the 5th prince.

09:36.110 --> 09:37.500
I don't think your father

09:37.900 --> 09:39.780
will disobey His Majesty.

09:41.470 --> 09:43.350
We'll be family soon.

09:43.900 --> 09:45.070
Just rest easy and wait

09:45.070 --> 09:46.310
to be my daughter-in-law.

09:50.860 --> 09:51.740
Your Grace,

09:52.350 --> 09:53.500
the edict hasn't been issued.

09:53.780 --> 09:55.070
Nothing is certain.

09:57.500 --> 10:00.230
I know Duan Xu also wants to marry you.

10:01.430 --> 10:03.230
But his family can't give any support

10:03.230 --> 10:04.620
to your family.

10:04.620 --> 10:07.430
Besides, Duan Xu is very arrogant.

10:07.430 --> 10:09.260
He'll get into trouble sooner or later.

10:11.140 --> 10:12.310
If you marry him,

10:13.350 --> 10:15.430
a sword will be hanging over your head.

10:17.310 --> 10:19.470
If he's caught in trouble,

10:20.740 --> 10:23.110
your family can't stay out of it.

10:24.540 --> 10:26.860
I believe you're clever enough.

10:28.590 --> 10:31.540
You will weigh the pros and cons.

10:52.740 --> 10:54.260
So it's you who have a treaty

10:54.990 --> 10:55.990
with Song Xingyu.

11:33.260 --> 11:34.260
Song Xingyu,

11:35.110 --> 11:36.260
trying to run away?

11:37.190 --> 11:38.030
Your...

11:38.780 --> 11:39.620
Your Lordship.

11:41.230 --> 11:42.660
I can no longer stay in this city.

11:43.140 --> 11:44.380
He... He Simu

11:44.380 --> 11:45.660
is going to find me.

11:45.830 --> 11:47.590
Don't forget our treaty.

11:48.230 --> 11:49.830
Even if you have the Glazed Pagoda,

11:50.260 --> 11:52.140
I can still find you.

11:53.590 --> 11:54.950
I... I'll give you

11:54.950 --> 11:56.110
all the puppet spirits

11:56.780 --> 11:57.620
I've made.

11:58.310 --> 11:59.310
Please let me go.

12:03.260 --> 12:04.710
Let me leave this city.

12:05.860 --> 12:06.860
Otherwise, He Simu

12:07.140 --> 12:08.140
will kill me.

12:11.590 --> 12:12.950
Our great plan is nearly complete.

12:13.690 --> 12:14.540
Once it's complete,

12:14.540 --> 12:16.430
you no longer need to hide.

12:16.990 --> 12:18.110
And I'll double the treasures

12:18.110 --> 12:19.660
I've promised you.

12:20.430 --> 12:22.190
Keep collecting Spirit Aura for me.

12:22.660 --> 12:23.860
I'll handle

12:24.190 --> 12:25.190
Her Grace.

12:30.950 --> 12:32.140
During our last meeting,

12:32.900 --> 12:34.140
I left without telling you.

12:35.710 --> 12:37.110
So I came to apologize.

12:39.830 --> 12:41.660
No need to apologize, Mr. Duan.

12:49.230 --> 12:50.710
Mother told me

12:51.350 --> 12:53.380
that you went after some bandits.

12:53.900 --> 12:55.310
State affairs come first.

12:57.590 --> 12:59.190
That's not true.

12:59.830 --> 13:01.470
I just saw my beloved lady.

13:04.950 --> 13:06.140
Do you know the plan

13:06.140 --> 13:07.540
of our fathers?

13:09.590 --> 13:10.740
In this city,

13:11.710 --> 13:12.740
only a few people

13:13.380 --> 13:14.710
are of marriageable age.

13:15.500 --> 13:16.740
We don't have many choices.

13:19.260 --> 13:20.100
So Miss Wang...

13:23.900 --> 13:24.990
How about you marry me?

13:44.990 --> 13:45.830
Your Lordship,

13:46.020 --> 13:47.110
a letter from Consort Yu.

13:50.140 --> 13:52.300
(To Duke Pei)

13:55.620 --> 13:57.580
(Wang and Duan will get married.
Do something.)

13:59.660 --> 14:00.540
Get Fang Ji to me.

14:01.230 --> 14:02.070
Yes.

14:16.900 --> 14:17.740
Great Ancestor,

14:18.110 --> 14:19.780
what did I tell you that day?

14:19.990 --> 14:21.660
They're finally in love, aren't they?

14:41.380 --> 14:42.230
Oh, Great Ancestor.

14:43.310 --> 14:44.310
I often think

14:44.310 --> 14:45.950
you're more human than I am.

14:46.780 --> 14:47.620
Ziji, look.

14:47.830 --> 14:49.830
The plantain's color doesn't look

14:50.230 --> 14:52.110
like something a spirit
who can't see colors

14:52.110 --> 14:53.190
would paint.

14:56.230 --> 14:57.070
It's beautiful.

14:59.430 --> 15:01.590
That's because you're lazy, ignorant,

15:01.590 --> 15:02.660
inattentive,

15:02.660 --> 15:03.660
and unsuccessful.

15:09.950 --> 15:11.070
But in my opinion,

15:11.950 --> 15:13.860
it doesn't matter

15:14.470 --> 15:16.470
whether poor General Duan loves her.

15:16.830 --> 15:18.020
He must marry someone

15:18.020 --> 15:19.430
his clan and Chancellor Du

15:19.430 --> 15:20.270
have designated.

15:24.830 --> 15:25.670
What?

15:26.590 --> 15:28.710
You don't think so?

15:30.500 --> 15:31.740
You don't know Duan Xu.

15:34.350 --> 15:36.070
If I did,

15:36.620 --> 15:37.860
what should I think?

15:43.350 --> 15:45.070
He's best at pretending to obey.

15:46.780 --> 15:48.140
No one can make him do anything

15:48.140 --> 15:49.620
he doesn't want to do.

15:50.190 --> 15:51.190
And he won't marry anyone

15:51.190 --> 15:52.070
he doesn't like.

15:53.190 --> 15:54.310
Something about that girl

15:54.310 --> 15:55.620
must have attracted him.

15:55.860 --> 15:56.740
Or she can help him

15:56.740 --> 15:57.710
fulfill his wish.

15:59.110 --> 16:00.540
He won't let himself be mistreated.

16:02.190 --> 16:04.020
I've never seen you

16:04.540 --> 16:05.710
so patient and familiar

16:05.860 --> 16:08.020
with a mortal.

16:18.310 --> 16:19.310
I care about him.

16:23.950 --> 16:24.860
But this care

16:24.860 --> 16:25.830
is only temporary.

16:28.260 --> 16:29.710
It's even shorter

16:29.710 --> 16:30.710
than his fleeting life.

16:38.070 --> 16:38.910
That's too bad.

16:39.310 --> 16:41.020
Duan Xu will have bad luck.

16:41.740 --> 16:43.070
The court is in turmoil.

16:43.070 --> 16:43.950
His marriage

16:43.950 --> 16:45.350
may be a bumpy ride.

16:46.140 --> 16:47.540
He'll have to miss

16:47.540 --> 16:48.590
the lucky day I picked.

16:51.190 --> 16:52.030
Great Ancestor,

16:52.900 --> 16:54.110
will you really not

16:54.620 --> 16:55.990
steal the bridegroom?

17:03.070 --> 17:03.910
Get lost.

17:21.990 --> 17:22.830
Assassin!

17:22.830 --> 17:23.720
Protect Mr. Fang!

17:26.170 --> 17:27.040
Something's not right.

17:27.050 --> 17:27.960
Don't come out here.

17:40.740 --> 17:41.580
Leave now!

17:41.710 --> 17:42.550
Leave!

18:07.780 --> 18:08.620
Who wants me dead?

18:09.260 --> 18:10.990
Obviously my father, who sees you

18:12.540 --> 18:13.380
as a major threat.

18:30.230 --> 18:31.070
Nice to meet you.

18:32.580 --> 18:33.420
I'm Duan Xu,

18:34.500 --> 18:35.470
D-U-A-N, X-U.

18:38.910 --> 18:40.100
My father, Duan Chengzhang,

18:41.150 --> 18:41.990
wants you dead.

18:49.950 --> 18:50.950
I read your essays.

18:52.630 --> 18:53.470
They're excellent.

18:54.780 --> 18:56.500
They shouldn't disappear from the world.

18:58.540 --> 19:00.430
You should uphold justice

19:02.340 --> 19:03.540
and give people a good life

19:04.710 --> 19:05.820
as the sages said.

19:07.710 --> 19:08.550
I've heard weapons

19:09.300 --> 19:10.140
are the tool of evil

19:10.740 --> 19:11.580
or virtue.

19:12.340 --> 19:13.470
I'll be the tool of evil.

19:15.340 --> 19:16.470
You'll be the tool of virtue.

19:19.150 --> 19:19.990
What do you say?

19:28.190 --> 19:29.190
So he hates me that much.

19:31.540 --> 19:32.710
You've begun to shine.

19:33.470 --> 19:35.020
You'll just be in more danger.

19:36.260 --> 19:37.100
Shall I get Luoxian

19:37.100 --> 19:38.190
out of Yuzao Pleasure House

19:38.710 --> 19:39.740
to protect you for now?

19:39.910 --> 19:40.870
No way.

19:40.870 --> 19:42.820
The court is in turmoil.

19:43.540 --> 19:44.390
We need her intel

19:44.390 --> 19:45.540
from Yuzao Pleasure House.

19:46.630 --> 19:48.070
Oh, I have something to tell you.

19:51.260 --> 19:52.540
The corruption case took a turn.

19:53.300 --> 19:54.710
Sun Changde of the Imperial Stud

19:54.910 --> 19:55.750
backtracked.

19:57.870 --> 19:58.990
Did he say

19:59.430 --> 20:00.990
the 3,000 warhorses weren't phantoms,

20:01.300 --> 20:02.300
but died of plague?

20:03.100 --> 20:03.940
Something worse.

20:04.250 --> 20:05.100
He even said

20:05.120 --> 20:06.740
someone threatened and ordered him

20:06.990 --> 20:08.260
to report this case to frame

20:08.710 --> 20:09.990
the Minister of the Imperial Stud

20:09.990 --> 20:10.990
and the Minister of War.

20:11.870 --> 20:12.710
I guess Duke Pei

20:12.990 --> 20:13.910
ordered him

20:13.910 --> 20:14.750
to backtrack.

20:16.260 --> 20:17.100
You and I both know

20:17.300 --> 20:18.820
the corruption case is absolutely true.

20:19.430 --> 20:20.270
But you forged

20:20.280 --> 20:21.390
some of the evidence.

20:21.950 --> 20:22.870
If they dig further,

20:22.870 --> 20:24.190
they'll trace it back to you.

20:25.470 --> 20:26.310
Let's take things

20:26.950 --> 20:27.790
as they come.

20:28.230 --> 20:29.070
Soon,

20:29.260 --> 20:30.470
things will turn around.

20:31.950 --> 20:32.790
Oh,

20:33.060 --> 20:34.150
let me introduce someone.

20:34.870 --> 20:35.710
Now?

20:37.870 --> 20:38.710
Right here?

20:39.630 --> 20:40.470
Someone

20:40.480 --> 20:41.340
who matters most.

20:43.740 --> 20:44.710
Someone I can't let go of

20:47.710 --> 20:48.910
after trying really hard.

20:54.190 --> 20:55.030
He Simu.

21:12.100 --> 21:12.940
Simu,

21:13.580 --> 21:14.990
can you show my friend

21:15.260 --> 21:16.340
your true form too?

21:29.500 --> 21:30.340
Simu,

21:31.300 --> 21:32.300
this is my close friend,

21:32.500 --> 21:33.340
Fang Xianye.

21:33.990 --> 21:34.830
Xianye,

21:35.300 --> 21:36.390
this is He Simu,

21:36.710 --> 21:37.550
Sovereign of Spirits.

21:37.710 --> 21:38.630
Sovereign?

21:40.430 --> 21:41.430
Why did you call me out?

21:42.430 --> 21:43.540
I didn't give you the right

21:44.150 --> 21:44.990
to summon me

21:44.990 --> 21:45.850
for fun.

21:47.430 --> 21:48.630
I want to make a deal.

21:51.540 --> 21:52.380
What conditions?

21:59.260 --> 22:00.340
You come to my wedding.

22:06.430 --> 22:07.270
Simu,

22:09.300 --> 22:10.820
I want you to come to my wedding

22:12.340 --> 22:13.340
as part of our deal.

22:20.590 --> 22:23.530
♪I go alone in the night without end♪

22:23.830 --> 22:27.330
♪I can't remember the seasons
or the passing years♪

22:28.310 --> 22:30.680
♪Wishful thoughts creep onto my brows♪

22:30.700 --> 22:31.540
Are you sure

22:31.990 --> 22:33.150
you won't use this deal

22:33.150 --> 22:34.740
on something more valuable?

22:35.150 --> 22:35.990
Valuable?

22:37.470 --> 22:38.910
I want you to see me in my wedding gown.

22:39.540 --> 22:40.630
It's once in a lifetime.

22:41.540 --> 22:42.580
Isn't it valuable?

22:43.270 --> 22:45.570
♪Countless wayfarers roam the world♪

22:45.650 --> 22:49.910
♪Luckily, I share a fate with you♪

22:49.990 --> 22:50.830
Here, the invitation.

22:52.430 --> 22:53.340
I humbly invite you.

22:54.500 --> 22:55.870
On the 18th day of the sixth month,

22:56.500 --> 22:57.340
the banquet will be served at my place.

22:58.710 --> 22:59.950
I look forward to your presence.

23:02.260 --> 23:03.390
May it bring joy

23:04.710 --> 23:05.910
and lead to a blessed union.

23:06.230 --> 23:07.140
♪But I fear♪

23:07.140 --> 23:10.120
♪The world can't hold them♪

23:10.320 --> 23:12.920
♪You always stay with me♪

23:13.060 --> 23:13.900
Please don't decline.

23:14.160 --> 23:17.910
♪See the world I've never seen♪

23:18.590 --> 23:22.620
♪However the years may wind♪

23:23.260 --> 23:24.100
All right.

23:25.390 --> 23:26.230
I'll go.

23:32.230 --> 23:33.150
Foxy.

23:37.430 --> 23:38.270
Congratulations.

23:56.780 --> 24:00.120
♪I open my eyes♪

24:01.190 --> 24:02.060
Who is she?

24:05.390 --> 24:06.260
My beloved woman.

24:07.580 --> 24:08.420
Woman?

24:08.910 --> 24:09.870
She isn't even human.

24:10.990 --> 24:11.910
Could she be a spirit?

24:12.670 --> 24:13.540
You told me she was...

24:13.540 --> 24:14.380
Fang Ji,

24:15.430 --> 24:16.630
how about you have a child

24:17.470 --> 24:18.580
and I'm his honorary father?

24:20.060 --> 24:20.900
Or...

24:21.500 --> 24:22.540
If you don't mind,

24:23.300 --> 24:24.230
let me adopt him.

24:24.990 --> 24:25.830
A madman like you

24:26.150 --> 24:26.990
should end up alone.

24:30.900 --> 24:33.180
(Yueran Fragrance)

24:33.190 --> 24:34.030
Master Xuan,

24:34.670 --> 24:36.390
get me some superb amber.

24:39.190 --> 24:40.030
Master Xuan?

24:43.260 --> 24:44.100
It's you, Miss Duan.

24:44.670 --> 24:45.510
Want ingredients?

24:46.710 --> 24:47.710
Get me the best amber

24:47.710 --> 24:48.950
for my fragrant powder.

24:49.710 --> 24:50.780
I will make

24:51.190 --> 24:53.100
the finest and sweetest powder

24:53.910 --> 24:55.300
and wear the newest style of clothes

24:56.150 --> 24:57.820
for my brother's wedding.

25:07.300 --> 25:08.910
Make an identical sachet for me.

25:09.300 --> 25:11.190
The ingredients are agarwood, amber,

25:11.200 --> 25:12.650
storax, mint leaves,

25:12.650 --> 25:13.670
bletilla, and benzoin.

25:14.020 --> 25:14.860
All right.

25:19.100 --> 25:19.940
Miss Duan,

25:21.390 --> 25:22.230
please wait a minute.

25:40.740 --> 25:42.020
Why do you stare at me?

25:44.870 --> 25:46.100
I think your sachet

25:46.500 --> 25:47.820
smells very good.

25:48.580 --> 25:50.190
Did you blend the fragrance yourself?

25:50.820 --> 25:52.060
What's its name?

25:54.870 --> 25:55.740
Duan Shunxi.

26:04.580 --> 26:05.430
It's done, Miss.

26:10.540 --> 26:11.380
Hey, wait.

26:12.390 --> 26:13.780
It doesn't smell right.

26:27.500 --> 26:28.540
The bletilla is missing.

26:29.670 --> 26:30.510
Miss Duan.

26:35.630 --> 26:37.070
Sorry, Miss. I'll add it now.

26:49.710 --> 26:50.550
Thank you.

26:59.060 --> 27:00.150
(Maybe she's someone)

27:00.540 --> 27:02.190
(who adores my brother.)

27:08.710 --> 27:09.550
Master Xuan.

27:10.740 --> 27:12.390
You don't look very well today.

27:12.670 --> 27:13.580
Take care of yourself.

27:17.020 --> 27:18.100
Young Master Xu's wedding

27:19.020 --> 27:20.020
is a grand event in town.

27:23.100 --> 27:24.300
You must be working hard on it.

27:24.950 --> 27:26.100
Take care of yourself too.

27:26.470 --> 27:27.310
Thank you.

27:28.540 --> 27:29.380
Biqing.

27:39.540 --> 27:40.710
That lady

27:40.710 --> 27:41.780
somehow got to know

27:41.780 --> 27:43.430
your aromatic ingredients.

27:43.580 --> 27:45.870
Then she had the identical fragrance.

27:46.540 --> 27:47.740
It will make her think of you.

27:49.740 --> 27:50.580
Come on, Xu.

27:50.780 --> 27:51.710
Your marriage

27:51.710 --> 27:53.950
will break the heart
of young ladies in town.

27:55.820 --> 27:56.670
Handsome disaster.

27:57.390 --> 27:58.260
Are you saying

27:58.260 --> 27:59.470
an ingredient was missing

27:59.820 --> 28:00.710
and she didn't realize?

28:01.710 --> 28:02.550
Strange, isn't it?

28:06.990 --> 28:07.830
How lovely.

28:16.710 --> 28:17.550
Hey, Xu.

28:18.230 --> 28:19.580
You're getting married.

28:19.710 --> 28:20.990
You must not

28:20.990 --> 28:22.190
find other girls lovely.

28:29.950 --> 28:30.790
Xu,

28:31.670 --> 28:32.740
didn't you say

28:33.670 --> 28:35.150
you loved someone?

28:36.740 --> 28:38.100
Are you giving up on her?

28:54.630 --> 28:55.770
Look, Xu.

28:56.340 --> 28:57.950
This is my new sachet.

28:58.230 --> 28:59.070
Smell it.

29:04.470 --> 29:05.310
What do you think?

29:08.230 --> 29:09.070
Mimosa flower.

29:09.740 --> 29:10.580
Eupatorium.

29:11.230 --> 29:12.070
Fleeceflower vine.

29:12.580 --> 29:13.420
Magnolia flower bud.

29:15.260 --> 29:16.100
Agastache.

29:21.230 --> 29:22.070
That's all?

29:22.340 --> 29:23.180
Yes.

29:23.630 --> 29:24.780
Two more.

29:25.430 --> 29:27.470
Fennel and lily.

29:33.670 --> 29:35.340
Well, mistakes happen.

29:36.740 --> 29:37.740
(I can't smell it all.)

29:40.230 --> 29:42.060
(So this is the price
of exchanging senses.)

29:55.870 --> 29:57.260
I'm getting old, anyway.

29:58.060 --> 29:58.900
Jingyuan,

29:59.430 --> 30:00.340
I'm afraid

30:00.340 --> 30:01.910
I'll often make mistakes in this game.

30:02.190 --> 30:03.150
You're still young.

30:03.500 --> 30:04.780
Don't say that.

30:05.540 --> 30:06.430
Age always

30:06.950 --> 30:08.470
weakens the senses.

30:09.340 --> 30:10.230
That's a natural rule.

30:18.820 --> 30:21.060
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

30:27.260 --> 30:28.100
Great Ancestor?

30:30.430 --> 30:31.340
Great Ancestor,

30:31.340 --> 30:32.190
where have you been?

30:33.500 --> 30:34.340
I bought a sachet.

30:35.990 --> 30:37.500
You can't smell anything.

30:37.500 --> 30:38.780
Why do you need a sachet?

30:39.740 --> 30:40.710
I can't smell.

30:40.880 --> 30:41.740
But I like it

30:41.740 --> 30:42.740
when this scent is on me.

30:42.870 --> 30:43.710
Any problem?

30:43.870 --> 30:44.710
No, no.

30:49.580 --> 30:51.430
What kind of gifts

30:52.190 --> 30:53.430
do mortals give for a wedding?

30:54.820 --> 30:56.780
It depends on whose wedding it is.

31:01.340 --> 31:03.190
You won't give Duan Xu a gift, will you?

31:03.990 --> 31:05.820
He invited me to his wedding.

31:05.820 --> 31:07.020
I can't go without a gift.

31:10.670 --> 31:13.020
Come on, Great Ancestor.

31:13.340 --> 31:14.470
You always hate

31:14.470 --> 31:16.100
going to weddings or funerals.

31:16.260 --> 31:18.150
You didn't even attend
the wedding or funeral

31:18.150 --> 31:19.260
of my parents.

31:20.150 --> 31:21.100
You really

31:21.540 --> 31:22.540
favor him

31:23.230 --> 31:24.070
and prioritize love.

31:25.230 --> 31:26.070
He's different.

31:27.260 --> 31:28.740
It's his condition for sense exchange.

31:29.910 --> 31:31.020
I've realized

31:31.300 --> 31:33.060
you're tolerant of him for no reason.

31:36.150 --> 31:37.190
This is just a deal.

31:38.990 --> 31:40.910
I happened to prepare

31:40.910 --> 31:42.230
a big gift for him.

31:43.190 --> 31:44.390
The horse administration case

31:44.390 --> 31:45.540
is being investigated.

31:45.910 --> 31:47.150
The key witness backtracked,

31:47.150 --> 31:48.000
accusing Duan Xu

31:48.000 --> 31:49.500
of forging some evidence

31:49.500 --> 31:50.630
to attack the two cities.

31:50.910 --> 31:51.760
Duke Pei's men

31:51.760 --> 31:53.100
are keeping an eye

31:53.100 --> 31:53.940
on this case.

31:53.950 --> 31:54.910
I guess they'll probably

31:55.060 --> 31:56.540
give him more trouble.

31:56.820 --> 31:57.660
And I...

32:01.950 --> 32:04.260
What I'm working on

32:04.820 --> 32:06.780
can do Duan Xu a big favor.

32:12.430 --> 32:13.500
This is your gift.

32:14.990 --> 32:16.670
What should I give him?

32:16.990 --> 32:18.820
You've been getting along with him.

32:18.820 --> 32:20.300
Don't you know what he likes?

32:23.300 --> 32:24.340
Come on, Great Ancestor.

32:24.780 --> 32:25.870
When you gave gifts,

32:25.870 --> 32:27.340
you used to be decisive.

32:27.710 --> 32:29.500
Why are you so cautious now?

32:29.990 --> 32:32.100
You still have some days.

32:32.260 --> 32:34.150
It's hard to prepare a gift

32:34.950 --> 32:36.580
that brings real joy.

32:49.580 --> 32:50.420
That's right.

32:52.630 --> 32:53.500
Farewell.

33:22.470 --> 33:24.340
The Fire Star is off track.

33:26.230 --> 33:28.710
A lucky day is coming.

33:39.820 --> 33:40.740
Young Master Xu,

33:40.870 --> 33:42.100
want to see the top beauty?

33:42.740 --> 33:43.580
Unfortunately,

33:43.600 --> 33:44.610
she was bored with stories

33:44.670 --> 33:45.870
and then left this place.

33:46.060 --> 33:47.630
I'm here for Luoxian.

33:48.780 --> 33:49.710
But Young Master,

33:49.710 --> 33:51.500
Luoxian is receiving an important guest.

33:51.670 --> 33:52.540
She can't see you now.

33:54.470 --> 33:55.310
Mr. Duan.

34:10.990 --> 34:11.830
Mr. Duan.

34:14.140 --> 34:14.990
Luoxian,

34:15.270 --> 34:16.180
Mr. Duan...

34:16.580 --> 34:18.220
I must see Luoxian today.

34:20.470 --> 34:21.620
Mr. Fang, do you mind?

34:25.620 --> 34:27.020
Don't be angry, gentlemen.

34:27.910 --> 34:29.870
Sharing music is also a pleasure.

34:30.500 --> 34:33.540
I'd like to play music and sing for you.

35:10.580 --> 35:14.380
(Wang Jin, Vice Minister
of the Judicial Review)

35:20.470 --> 35:21.750
What a nice day today.

35:22.700 --> 35:23.830
The top three scholars

35:23.990 --> 35:25.060
of the same imperial exam

35:25.060 --> 35:25.900
are all here.

35:27.620 --> 35:29.140
Shall we close the net?

35:29.430 --> 35:30.620
I've prepared the net

35:30.990 --> 35:31.830
and had it in place.

35:32.220 --> 35:33.390
I've heated the stove

35:33.580 --> 35:34.430
with the ingredients.

35:34.750 --> 35:35.700
We're waiting for you.

35:37.350 --> 35:38.310
The fish is in the net.

35:38.790 --> 35:39.630
We'll close the net

35:40.220 --> 35:41.060
and eat the fish.

35:42.830 --> 35:43.670
To Great Liang.

35:44.390 --> 35:45.580
To people in the 17 Prefectures.

35:48.220 --> 35:54.740
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

35:59.870 --> 36:00.870
- Prophet.
- Prophet.

36:01.540 --> 36:02.380
Hey, destined one.

36:03.580 --> 36:04.790
Won't you return the umbrella?

36:26.310 --> 36:27.620
Give this umbrella to the Prophet.

36:28.350 --> 36:29.660
Tell him Duan Shunxi came by.

36:30.700 --> 36:31.990
The destined one must return

36:31.990 --> 36:34.060
the Red Lotus Umbrella himself.

36:34.870 --> 36:35.790
This way, please.

37:12.140 --> 37:13.540
This place is impressive.

37:14.310 --> 37:15.310
It takes a lot of trouble

37:15.750 --> 37:17.100
to see you.

37:18.870 --> 37:20.700
One must let go of his worries

37:20.990 --> 37:22.790
before he finds peace in himself.

37:23.580 --> 37:24.470
Every step here

37:25.100 --> 37:26.390
will erase a lie.

37:27.180 --> 37:29.020
There are white lotuses
in the front pond

37:29.540 --> 37:31.180
and red lotuses
in the hidden inner pond.

37:32.140 --> 37:33.910
This pavilion divides this place

37:33.910 --> 37:35.350
just like dividing one's heart.

37:35.870 --> 37:37.020
One side is full of peace

37:37.500 --> 37:38.830
while the other is full of heat.

37:39.700 --> 37:41.470
But you've never believed in gods.

37:41.790 --> 37:43.350
Sorry to have you come

37:43.790 --> 37:45.140
to my Lotusborn Pavilion.

37:53.180 --> 37:54.620
Since you're here,

37:55.140 --> 37:56.830
ask me what has confused you.

37:57.950 --> 37:58.790
For example,

37:59.580 --> 38:01.060
what's the relationship

38:01.060 --> 38:02.620
between He Simu and me?

38:05.540 --> 38:06.620
Since you know what I want

38:06.910 --> 38:07.790
and you're prepared,

38:09.020 --> 38:09.870
tell me about it.

38:10.910 --> 38:11.750
You should know

38:12.660 --> 38:14.180
He Simu had four family members.

38:15.020 --> 38:16.620
Her parents, her aunt, and her uncle.

38:17.310 --> 38:18.150
I am

38:18.750 --> 38:20.020
the twentieth generation

38:20.020 --> 38:21.430
of her aunt and uncle.

38:22.350 --> 38:25.470
In private, I call her Great Ancestor.

38:28.990 --> 38:29.910
My parents died young.

38:30.250 --> 38:31.090
When I was little,

38:31.090 --> 38:32.660
she took care of me for a while.

38:33.220 --> 38:34.580
She watched me grow up.

38:36.580 --> 38:38.100
Actually, I invited you here

38:38.750 --> 38:40.100
because I prepared a gift

38:40.100 --> 38:40.940
for your wedding.

38:42.470 --> 38:43.310
Ziji.

38:51.580 --> 38:52.470
(In the fifth month, spring ends)

38:52.830 --> 38:53.790
(and peonies fall.)

38:55.700 --> 38:56.540
Everyone knows

38:57.660 --> 38:58.660
Consort Yu loves peonies most.

39:01.270 --> 39:02.110
Are you saying

39:02.700 --> 39:03.540
the 5th prince...?

39:04.020 --> 39:05.750
I heard you have a photographic memory.

39:06.470 --> 39:07.750
So you don't need it again.

39:14.830 --> 39:15.870
Thank you for your help.

39:17.950 --> 39:19.180
Is this your gift?

39:20.220 --> 39:22.270
- Or...
- Great Ancestor never cares

39:22.270 --> 39:23.310
about politics.

39:23.540 --> 39:24.500
I'm the one

39:24.500 --> 39:25.340
who prepared this.

39:30.580 --> 39:31.580
But we're strangers.

39:32.350 --> 39:33.190
Why do you help me?

39:34.700 --> 39:36.060
I don't mean to help you.

39:37.620 --> 39:38.500
When I was little,

39:39.990 --> 39:41.020
I secretly found a journal

39:41.020 --> 39:42.310
of Great Ancestor.

39:43.500 --> 39:45.390
The one in that journal

39:46.310 --> 39:47.750
was totally different

39:48.350 --> 39:49.500
from what she is now.

39:51.220 --> 39:53.140
The young girl named He Simu

39:53.660 --> 39:54.500
was arrogant

39:55.390 --> 39:56.230
and spoiled.

39:58.020 --> 39:58.870
Her mother said

39:59.430 --> 40:00.870
red suited her best.

40:01.540 --> 40:02.470
So she made

40:02.470 --> 40:04.180
over a dozen red robes.

40:08.470 --> 40:10.020
She actually couldn't see colors.

40:15.180 --> 40:16.270
But she said she loved them.

40:19.100 --> 40:19.950
The journal was thick.

40:20.870 --> 40:22.220
It recorded

40:22.220 --> 40:23.180
small daily routines.

40:24.830 --> 40:25.670
About friends,

40:25.990 --> 40:26.830
about families,

40:27.470 --> 40:28.310
and about partners.

40:29.100 --> 40:31.990
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

40:31.990 --> 40:34.850
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

40:34.870 --> 40:36.140
One page said,

40:38.540 --> 40:39.380
"Father died.

40:39.990 --> 40:40.830
I'd return to the Spirit World."

40:40.830 --> 40:42.940
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

40:42.990 --> 40:44.430
Then nothing more was recorded.

40:46.910 --> 40:48.060
I used to think

40:48.060 --> 40:49.100
Great Ancestor was weird.

40:49.700 --> 40:50.910
But I couldn't tell

40:50.910 --> 40:51.950
what was weird about her.

40:52.950 --> 40:53.870
After reading that,

40:53.870 --> 40:55.020
I suddenly realized

40:55.500 --> 40:56.830
that time had long stopped

40:56.830 --> 40:57.950
for her.

40:58.390 --> 40:59.660
It stopped 300 years ago

40:59.660 --> 41:01.140
when her father passed away.

41:03.180 --> 41:06.710
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

41:07.220 --> 41:08.310
She still wears

41:08.310 --> 41:09.500
her favorite clothes

41:10.470 --> 41:11.790
and does things

41:11.790 --> 41:12.990
her family members taught her

41:13.270 --> 41:14.750
and expected her to do.

41:17.620 --> 41:19.620
She's becoming unfamiliar

41:20.790 --> 41:21.870
with this changing world.

41:22.540 --> 41:23.380
She's angry

41:23.540 --> 41:24.380
and frustrated.

41:26.310 --> 41:27.180
Just like the journal

41:27.180 --> 41:28.830
that stopped abruptly.

41:29.660 --> 41:31.660
When the last two lines were written...

41:33.760 --> 41:36.020
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

41:36.060 --> 41:37.660
She no longer needed to be understood.

41:39.020 --> 41:40.390
She only needed to be feared.

41:42.270 --> 41:43.430
She buried those she valued

41:43.910 --> 41:44.870
in the journal

41:44.870 --> 41:46.270
and froze everything in time.

41:47.540 --> 41:48.790
Over the past 300 years,

41:50.430 --> 41:51.750
no one has entered her world.

41:52.890 --> 41:56.830
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

41:56.970 --> 41:59.530
♪As all things turn and flow♪

41:59.750 --> 42:02.740
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

42:02.740 --> 42:03.580
(Sovereign's Hall)

42:04.620 --> 42:05.460
Mr. Duan,

42:06.310 --> 42:07.790
either you're her spell bearer

42:07.790 --> 42:08.790
or whatever,

42:09.790 --> 42:10.870
I want you

42:10.870 --> 42:12.350
to get her frozen time

42:12.350 --> 42:13.190
to move again.

42:14.100 --> 42:14.940
This is

42:15.950 --> 42:17.430
why I'm helping you.

42:19.840 --> 42:23.440
♪As stars shift and change places♪

42:23.610 --> 42:27.290
♪A century is like a dream♪

42:27.610 --> 42:30.970
♪Let me journey across them all♪

42:31.140 --> 42:31.980
Thank you, Prophet.

42:36.500 --> 42:37.340
In that case,

42:38.870 --> 42:40.140
I have another favor to ask.

42:40.830 --> 42:41.670
What is it?

42:42.140 --> 42:43.470
Her Grace has a pearl.

42:44.060 --> 42:45.100
She and I exchange senses

42:45.580 --> 42:46.660
via the Pearl.

42:47.180 --> 42:48.100
Do you know about that?

42:48.580 --> 42:50.180
I know it very well.

42:52.870 --> 42:53.870
I want you

42:54.750 --> 42:55.990
to give me a blessed flower.

43:04.281 --> 43:09.611
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:09.941 --> 43:14.191
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:15.551 --> 43:20.921
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:21.221 --> 43:25.821
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:26.911 --> 43:28.751
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:40.961 --> 43:46.401
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:46.581 --> 43:50.911
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:52.281 --> 43:57.671
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:57.901 --> 44:01.841
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:03.611 --> 44:05.501
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:08.161 --> 44:11.321
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:11.321 --> 44:13.851
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:13.851 --> 44:19.371
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:19.371 --> 44:22.611
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:22.611 --> 44:27.471
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:27.811 --> 44:30.831
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:30.831 --> 44:33.651
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:33.911 --> 44:36.441
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:36.441 --> 44:41.861
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:42.031 --> 44:45.101
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

44:45.261 --> 44:50.161
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

44:50.371 --> 44:53.841
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
